        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", 162, 165. In which of these it is to be taken here is disputed. Dillm., after stating that in D ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Tôrah",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " is distinguished from Law proper, described as ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
