        "text": " is parallel to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "statutes and judgements",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". We may take it in the same sense here (so Driver), equivalent indeed to no mere catalogue of laws, but to laws with notes, exhortations, precedents and reminiscences. If that be the meaning of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
